      "text": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div id=\"infoboxborder\">\n<table id=\"infoboxtable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxheader\">Geode Crusher</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"padding-bottom: 5px; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"/File:Geode_Crusher.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Geode Crusher.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/0/02/Geode_Crusher.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"96\" /></a>&#160; &#160;<a href=\"/File:Geode_Crusher_On.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Geode Crusher On.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/1/13/Geode_Crusher_On.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"96\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxdetail\" style=\"text-align: center; font-style: italic; padding-right: 3px;\">Breaks geodes open automatically.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 0; padding-right: 0;\">Information</td>\n</tr>\n\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Source</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><a href=\"/Crafting\" title=\"Crafting\">Crafting</a></td>\n\t</tr> \n\t<tr>\n\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Sell Price</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><i>Cannot be sold</i>\n\t\t</td>\n</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 0; padding-right: 0;\">Crafting</td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Recipe Source</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><img alt=\"Clint Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/74/Clint_Icon.png/24px-Clint_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/7/74/Clint_Icon.png 1.5x\" /> <a href=\"/Quests#Cave_Patrol\" title=\"Quests\">\"Cave Patrol\"</a> Special Order</td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Ingredients</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120955\">.mw-parser-output .nametemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplate img,.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Gold Bar.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/4e/Gold_Bar.png/24px-Gold_Bar.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/4e/Gold_Bar.png/36px-Gold_Bar.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/4e/Gold_Bar.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Gold_Bar\" title=\"Gold Bar\">Gold Bar</a>&#160;(2)</span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Stone.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d4/Stone.png/24px-Stone.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d4/Stone.png/36px-Stone.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/d/d4/Stone.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Stone\" title=\"Stone\">Stone</a>&#160;(50)</span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Diamond.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/ea/Diamond.png/24px-Diamond.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/ea/Diamond.png/36px-Diamond.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/e/ea/Diamond.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Diamond\" title=\"Diamond\">Diamond</a>&#160;(1)</span></td>\n\t</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p>The <b>Geode Crusher</b> is a piece of <a href=\"/Crafting#Refining_Equipment\" title=\"Crafting\">Refining Equipment</a> that can be used to open <a href=\"/Minerals#Geodes\" title=\"Minerals\">geodes</a> on <a href=\"/The_Farm\" title=\"The Farm\">the Farm</a>. The player receives the recipe after completing <a href=\"/Clint\" title=\"Clint\">Clint</a>'s <a href=\"/Quests#List_of_Special_Orders\" title=\"Quests\">Special Order</a> <a href=\"/Quests#Cave_Patrol\" title=\"Quests\">\"Cave Patrol\"</a>. It takes <style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120974\">.mw-parser-output .durationtemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .durationtemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .durationtemplate img,.mw-parser-output .durationtemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"durationtemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Time Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/24px-Time_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/36px-Time_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/70/Time_Icon.png 2x\" /> 60m (1h)</span> to process.<sup id=\"cite_ref-processtime_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-processtime-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The Geode Crusher cannot open <a href=\"/Artifact_Trove\" title=\"Artifact Trove\">artifact troves</a>, <a href=\"/Golden_Coconut\" title=\"Golden Coconut\">golden coconuts</a>, <a href=\"/Mystery_Box\" title=\"Mystery Box\">mystery boxes</a>, or <a href=\"/Golden_Mystery_Box\" title=\"Golden Mystery Box\">golden mystery boxes</a>.\n</p><p>This item provides an alternative to paying <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"25\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />25g</span> for Clint <a href=\"/Blacksmith#Process_Geodes\" title=\"Blacksmith\">to open</a> 1 geode.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Geode_Crusher&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-processtime-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-processtime_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">See <samp>Object::performObjectDropInAction</samp> in the game code.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Geode_Crusher&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.5\" title=\"Version History\">1.5</a>: Introduced.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.6\" title=\"Version History\">1.6</a>: No longer requires <a href=\"/Coal\" title=\"Coal\">Coal</a> to operate. Fixed bug that caused the Geode Crusher to produce the same item if fed with the same type of <a href=\"/Minerals#Geodes\" title=\"Minerals\">geode</a> immediately after cracking one at the <a href=\"/Blacksmith\" title=\"Blacksmith\">Blacksmith</a>.</li></ul>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"3\">Equipment\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Crafting#Artisan_Equipment\" title=\"Crafting\">Artisan</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Bee_House\" title=\"Bee House\">Bee House</a> • <a href=\"/Cask\" title=\"Cask\">Cask</a> • <a href=\"/Cheese_Press\" title=\"Cheese Press\">Cheese Press</a> • <a href=\"/Dehydrator\" title=\"Dehydrator\">Dehydrator</a> • <a href=\"/Fish_Smoker\" title=\"Fish Smoker\">Fish Smoker</a> • <a href=\"/Keg\" title=\"Keg\">Keg</a> • <a href=\"/Loom\" title=\"Loom\">Loom</a> • <a href=\"/Mayonnaise_Machine\" title=\"Mayonnaise Machine\">Mayonnaise Machine</a> • <a href=\"/Oil_Maker\" title=\"Oil Maker\">Oil Maker</a> • <a href=\"/Preserves_Jar\" title=\"Preserves Jar\">Preserves Jar</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Crafting#Refining_Equipment\" title=\"Crafting\">Refining</a>\n</th>