      "wikitext": "{{Infobox\n|eng         = Geode Crusher\n|image2      = Geode Crusher On\n|image2spacing = true\n|source      = [[Crafting]]\n|recipe      = [[File:Clint Icon.png|24px|link=]] [[Quests#Cave Patrol|\"Cave Patrol\"]] Special Order\n|ingredients = {{Name|Gold Bar|2}}{{Name|Stone|50}}{{Name|Diamond|1}}\n|sellprice   = N/A\n}}\nThe '''Geode Crusher''' is a piece of [[Crafting#Refining Equipment|Refining Equipment]] that can be used to open [[Minerals#Geodes|geodes]] on [[the Farm]]. The player receives the recipe after completing [[Clint]]'s [[Quests#List of Special Orders|Special Order]] [[Quests#Cave Patrol|\"Cave Patrol\"]]. It takes {{duration|60m (1h)|class=inline}} to process.<ref name=\"processtime\"/>\n\nThe Geode Crusher cannot open [[Artifact Trove|artifact troves]], [[Golden Coconut|golden coconuts]], [[Mystery Box|mystery boxes]], or [[Golden Mystery Box|golden mystery boxes]].\n\nThis item provides an alternative to paying {{Price|25}} for Clint [[Blacksmith#Process Geodes|to open]] 1 geode.\n\n==References==\n<references>\n  <ref name=\"processtime\">See <samp>Object::performObjectDropInAction</samp> in the game code.</ref>\n</references>\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.5|Introduced.}}\n{{History|1.6|No longer requires [[Coal]] to operate. Fixed bug that caused the Geode Crusher to produce the same item if fed with the same type of [[Minerals#Geodes|geode]] immediately after cracking one at the [[Blacksmith]].}}\n\n{{NavboxEquipment}}\n\n[[Category:Craftable items]]\n\n[[de:Geoden Brecher]]\n[[es:Prensa de geodas]]\n[[fr:Broyeur de géode]]\n[[it:Spacca-geodi]]\n[[ja:ジオード粉砕機]]\n[[ko:정동석 분쇄기]]\n[[hu:Geóda zúzó]]\n[[pt:Esmagador de Geodos]]\n[[ru:Разбиватель жеод]]\n[[tr:Jeotkırar]]\n[[zh:晶球破开器]]"
